---
import FacebookIcon from "./FacebookIcon.astro";
---

<footer class="border-t border-coffee-900/10 bg-coffee-950 text-paper">
  <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-10 px-5 py-14 sm:px-8 md:grid-cols-3">
    <div>
      <img src="/logo.svg" alt="Kafé Borg" class="h-20 w-auto" />
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-xs font-body text-sm leading-relaxed text-paper/70">
        Family-run coffee roasters in San Gwann since Nicholas and Gaetano&rsquo;s
        great-grandfather started roasting. Same shop, same corner, same idea:
        good coffee, honestly priced.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h3 class="font-display text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-gold-300">
        Visit
      </h3>
      <address class="mt-4 space-y-1.5 font-body text-sm not-italic leading-relaxed text-paper/80">
        <p>Kaf&eacute; Borg</p>
        <p>Tal-Balal Road</p>
        <p>San Gwann SGN 9018, Malta</p>
      </address>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h3 class="font-display text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-gold-300">
        Get in touch
      </h3>
      <ul class="mt-4 space-y-1.5 font-body text-sm leading-relaxed text-paper/80">
        <li>
          <a href="tel:+35621371626" class="hover:text-gold-300">Phone: (+356) 2137 1626</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="tel:+35621373208" class="hover:text-gold-300">(+356) 2137 3208</a>
        </li>
        <li class="text-paper/60">Fax: (+356) 2137 1626</li>
        <li>
          <a href="mailto:info@kafeborg.com" class="hover:text-gold-300">info@kafeborg.com</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <a
        href="https://www.facebook.com/kafeborg"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        aria-label="Kafé Borg on Facebook"
        class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center text-paper/80 transition-colors hover:text-gold-300"
      >
        <FacebookIcon class="h-5 w-5" />
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div
    class="border-t border-paper/10 px-5 py-5 text-center font-body text-xs text-paper/50 sm:px-8"
  >
    <p>&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Kaf&eacute; Borg &middot; Roasted and ground on Tal-Balal Road, San Gwann</p>
  </div>
</footer>
